  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>

<body>

  <nav>
    <div id="nav-left">
      <div id="logo">
        <h1>Geldix</h1>
        <p>Pharmaceutical</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="nav-right">
      <h4>HOME</h4>
      <h4>PRODUCTS</h4>
      <h4>ABOUT US</h4>
      <h4>CONTACT US</h4>
      <i class="ri-menu-5-line"></i>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div id="main">
    <div id="home" data-scroll-section>
      <div id="home-left" data-scroll>
        <h1>Empowering Health, Enriching Lives</h1>
        <p>we are dedicated to enhancing lives through the provision of high-quality pharmaceutical products and
          healthcare solutions. With a steadfast commitment to innovation, excellence, and integrity, we strive to be a
          trusted partner in healthcare delivery worldwide.</p>
        <p>Driven by our mission to improve global health outcomes, Geldix Pharmaceuticals focuses on developing and
          delivering innovative medications and therapeutic solutions that address unmet medical needs. Our diverse
          portfolio encompasses a wide range of pharmaceutical products, including but not limited to prescription
          medicines, over-the-counter medications, and specialty therapies.</p>

      </div>
      <div id="home-right" data-scroll>
        <img src="/public/images/med.jpg" alt="">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="products-heading" data-scroll-section>
      <h1 data-scroll>OUR PRODUCTS</h1>
    </div>
    <div id="products" data-scroll-section>
      <% products.forEach(product=> { %>
        <a href="/products/<%= product._id %>" data-scroll>
          <div class="product-card">
            <img src="<%= product.image %>" alt="<%= product.productname %>">
            <p id="product-name">
              <%= product.productname %>
            </p>
            <p id="discounted-price">
              <%= product.productdescription %>
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <% }); %>
    </div>
    <div id="about-heading" data-scroll-section>
      <h1>ABOUT US</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="about" data-scroll-section>
      <div class="about-main about-left">
        <p>At Geldix Pharmaceuticals, we are dedicated to enhancing lives through the provision of high-quality
          pharmaceutical products and healthcare solutions. With a steadfast commitment to innovation, excellence, and
          integrity, we strive to be a trusted partner in healthcare delivery worldwide.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Driven by our mission to improve global health outcomes, Geldix Pharmaceuticals focuses on developing and
          delivering innovative medications and therapeutic solutions that address unmet medical needs. Our diverse
          portfolio encompasses a wide range of pharmaceutical products, including but not limited to prescription
          medicines, over-the-counter medications, and specialty therapies.</p>

      </div>
      <div class="about-main about-right">
        <p>At the heart of our operations lies a team of passionate professionals who are dedicated to advancing
          healthcare through research, development, manufacturing, and distribution. We adhere to stringent quality
          standards and regulatory requirements to ensure that our products meet the highest levels of safety, efficacy,
          and reliability.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Beyond our commitment to product excellence, Geldix Pharmaceuticals places a strong emphasis on customer
          satisfaction and patient well-being. We continuously strive to foster strong relationships with healthcare
          providers, pharmacies, and patients, ensuring accessibility and affordability of our medications.</p>

      </div>
      <div class="about-main about-left">
        <p>As a socially responsible company, we are deeply invested in giving back to the communities we serve. Through
          corporate social responsibility initiatives, philanthropic endeavors, and partnerships with healthcare
          organizations, we aim to make a positive impact on society and contribute to the betterment of public health.
        </p>
        <br>
        <p>Geldix Pharmaceuticals is poised to lead the way in shaping the future of healthcare, leveraging our
          expertise, resources, and innovative spirit to make a meaningful difference in the lives of individuals and
          communities worldwide. Join us on our journey as we continue to deliver excellence in pharmaceuticals and
          healthcare solutions, empowering healthier futures for all.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="contact-heading" data-scroll-section>
      <h1>CONTACT US</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-us" data-scroll-section>
      <div id="whatsapp">
        <i class="ri-whatsapp-line"></i>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919718164407?text=Hi+Geldix+Pharmaceutical" target="_blank">
          <h2>Whatsapp</h2>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div id="contact-form">
        <form action="mailto:aakashpatel6250@gmail.com" enctype="text/plain" method="POST">
          <label for="name">Name:</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required><br><br>

          <label for="email">Email:</label>
          <input type="text" id="email" name="email" required><br><br>

          <label for="message">Message:</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea><br><br>

          <button>Submit</button>
        </form>
      </div>

    </div>

    <footer data-scroll-section>
      <h4 id="copyright">Â©2024 Geldix Pharmaceutical. All Rights Reserved.</h4>
      <h4 id="devloped">Developed by <a href="">Aakash Patel</a></h4>
    </footer>
  </div>

